name: CBJ95 Cry Baby Junior Wah
details: Pedalboard-sized Cry BabyDesigned in collaboration with Pedaltrain, the Dunlop CBJ95 Cry Baby Junior boasts a pedalboard-sized enclosure and front-mounted jacks, enabling you to fit it ergonomically onto your board. Three switchable voices supply a useful array of modern and vintage wah tones. You also get a convenient on/off status LED to show you when the effect is engaged, thereby solving an age-old issue with vintage-style wah-wah pedals. If classic Cry Baby wahs are your thing, but you’re short on pedalboard space, the Cry Baby Junior is the perfect wah-wah pedal for you.
